snippet.title: The Walking Dead: Empires - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The Walking Dead: Empires is an upcoming play-to-earn MMORPG strategy game created by Ember Entertainment and brought to you by AMC and Gala Games.

By purchasing a Dead Land Claim in the Georgia Land Sale, future players can own a piece of the game, allowing them to benefit and earn rewards from the action on their land!

BUY LAND (while supplies last)
https://app.gala.games/games/the-walking-dead-empires

TWDE WEBSITE:
https://twdempires.game/

GALA GAMES PLATFORM:
https://gala.games/

#gaming #NFT #thewalkingdead
